# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# Allowed types:
# feat:     A new feature (minor release)
# fix:      A bug fix (patch release)
# perf:     Performance improvements (patch release)
# build:    Changes that affect build system or dependencies
# ci:       CI configuration changes
# docs:     Documentation only changes (no release)
# style:    Formatting, missing semi colons, etc (no release)
# refactor: Code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
# test:     Adding or correcting tests
# chore:    Maintenance tasks
# revert:   Reverts a previous commit
#
# Breaking changes:
# Add "BREAKING CHANGE:" in the footer
# or append "!" after type/scope
#
# Examples:
# feat(ui): add document export dialog
# fix(storage)!: change file path layout
# revert: feat(ui): add document export dialog
